## Privacy Policy for Pizza Rush

**Effective Date: [Insert Date]**

**Kama-3** ("we", "our", "us") is committed to protecting the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy describes how we handle the information collected when you use our game, **Pizza Rush**.

### 1. Target Audience

Pizza Rush is designed for players of all ages, including children aged 13 and below. We prioritize the safety and privacy of our young players and adhere to all applicable privacy laws and regulations.

### 2. No Advertisements

Pizza Rush does not contain any advertisements. We strive to provide a seamless and enjoyable gaming experience without the interruption or influence of ads.

### 3. Use of Local Device Storage

Pizza Rush uses local device storage to save game progress and settings. This means that all game data, including your progress, preferences, and settings, is stored directly on your device. This ensures that you can pick up where you left off every time you play the game.

### 4. Data Collection and Transmission

Pizza Rush does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data or game-related data to any servers or third parties. All game data is contained locally on your device, and no information is shared outside of the game.

### 5. Children’s Privacy

We take special precautions to protect the privacy of our younger players. In accordance with the Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA), we do not collect any personal information from children under the age of 13. Since the game does not collect or transmit data, parents can be assured that their children’s privacy is protected.

### 6. Security

While we do not collect personal data, we still implement security measures to protect the data stored on your device. We recommend that you also take steps to protect your device and data, such as using strong passwords and keeping your device software up to date.

### 7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the game and/or on our website, and the effective date will be updated accordingly. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.

### 8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our practices, please contact us at:

**Kama-3**  
Email: support@kama3.com  
Address: [Insert Address]

Thank you for playing Pizza Rush and trusting us with your gaming experience. We are committed to providing a safe and enjoyable environment for all our players.

